{
  "stem": "16106.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And every night, Paul von Ribbsdor used to come down and tell us that we shouldn't worry at all because they're going to defend us to the last.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Yeah, but they said that, which was very nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And once it was over, it was over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I mean, that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Once the happiness was over and [GERMAN] they called, was over, it was over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You were safe again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "For a while.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Then it was over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we went, we went home again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we were-- then we knew who was missing, who wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then the news came in what really happened out there where they take us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Somebody came back, crawled out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Always somebody who crawled out from under.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They had to go there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They had to undress in that cold, horrible thing, put all the clothes in one spot, line up against a trench and were machine gunned down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Not Germans, Latvians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Latvians were so clever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "They used to line up one after another and could, with one bullet, shoot two.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "As they were even exporting Latvians executioners to all over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "To Lithuania, to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They were very good at that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "When it got dark, they had them herded in their barrack and to wait till the light and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And there was this wonderful lady whose name I forget, forgot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But she had red hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And she collected all the little children around her and told them stories about whatever entertained them all night so they shouldn't be frightened.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I, I-- that is a very, a [BACKROUND NOISE] very touching picture to think of.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And in the morning, they walked them out again and they [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "There are pictures, photographs of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're sitting-- do you know those photographs where they're sitting, sitting naked?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
